Selenium 2.21

sudo easy_install lettuce
sudo easy_install selenium  
sudo easy_install pyvirtualdisplay
sudo apt-get install xvfb

Start a test using :

PYTHONPATH=.. lettuce features/user.featuree

Lettuce tests are in features/*.feature.
Actions for each step are in features/step_definitions/*_steps.py
Common actions are in xivo_lettuce/common_steps.py


If you need to display the browser update xivo_lettuce terrain.py and
install sudo apt-get install xserver-xephyr